---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BottomDrawer from '../../components/BottomDrawer.astro';
---

<Layout title="User Experience Patterns - Project - Nolan">
  <article class="concept-page">
    <header class="concept-header">
      <div class="concept-meta">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to Portfolio</a>
        <div class="concept-details">
          <span class="concept-year">2024</span>
          <span class="concept-type">Research Project</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1>User Experience Patterns</h1>
      <p class="concept-subtitle">A systematic study of emerging interaction patterns in modern digital interfaces</p>
    </header>

    <div class="concept-content">
      <div class="concept-overview">
        <p class="lead">Digital interfaces are evolving rapidly, with new interaction patterns emerging from mobile-first design, voice interfaces, and gesture-based controls. This research project catalogs and analyzes these patterns to understand their effectiveness and appropriate use cases.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-media">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/900/500?random=120" alt="UX pattern analysis visualization" />
        <p class="media-caption">Visual analysis of interaction pattern evolution over time</p>
      </div>

      <section class="pattern-category">
        <h2>Micro-Interactions</h2>
        <p>Small, purposeful animations that provide feedback and guide user behavior.</p>
        
        <div class="pattern-examples">
          <div class="pattern-card">
            <div class="pattern-demo micro-demo">
              <button class="demo-button" id="like-button">
                <span class="heart-icon">‚ô°</span>
                <span class="like-text">Like</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <h4>Progressive Heart Animation</h4>
            <p>Emotional feedback that builds user engagement through delightful micro-moments</p>
            <div class="pattern-metrics">
              <span class="metric">+23% engagement</span>
              <span class="metric">+45% retention</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pattern-card">
            <div class="pattern-demo">
              <div class="loading-states">
                <div class="skeleton-loader"></div>
                <div class="skeleton-loader short"></div>
                <div class="skeleton-loader medium"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h4>Skeleton Loading</h4>
            <p>Progressive disclosure that maintains context while content loads</p>
            <div class="pattern-metrics">
              <span class="metric">-34% bounce rate</span>
              <span class="metric">Better perceived performance</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pattern-card">
            <div class="pattern-demo">
              <div class="swipe-indicator">
                <div class="swipe-dots">
                  <span class="dot active"></span>
                  <span class="dot"></span>
                  <span class="dot"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="swipe-hint">‚Üê Swipe ‚Üí</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h4>Swipe Affordances</h4>
            <p>Visual cues that communicate gesture-based interactions</p>
            <div class="pattern-metrics">
              <span class="metric">+67% gesture discovery</span>
              <span class="metric">Reduced tutorial needs</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="pattern-category">
        <h2>Navigation Evolution</h2>
        <p>How users move through digital spaces is fundamentally changing with new interaction paradigms.</p>
        
        <div class="navigation-study">
          <div class="nav-comparison">
            <div class="nav-type">
              <h4>Traditional Tab Navigation</h4>
              <div class="nav-demo traditional-nav">
                <div class="tab active">Home</div>
                <div class="tab">Search</div>
                <div class="tab">Profile</div>
              </div>
              <div class="nav-stats">
                <div class="stat">
                  <span class="stat-value">2.3s</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Avg Task Time</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                  <span class="stat-value">73%</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Success Rate</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="nav-type">
              <h4>Contextual Action Navigation</h4>
              <div class="nav-demo contextual-nav">
                <div class="floating-action">
                  <div class="main-action">+</div>
                  <div class="sub-actions">
                    <div class="sub-action">üìù</div>
                    <div class="sub-action">üì∑</div>
                    <div class="sub-action">üéµ</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="nav-stats">
                <div class="stat">
                  <span class="stat-value">1.7s</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Avg Task Time</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                  <span class="stat-value">89%</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Success Rate</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="pattern-category">
        <h2>Accessibility-First Patterns</h2>
        <p>Interaction patterns designed from the ground up to be inclusive and accessible.</p>
        
        <div class="accessibility-patterns">
          <div class="a11y-pattern">
            <h4>Smart Focus Management</h4>
            <div class="pattern-demo focus-demo">
              <div class="modal-simulation">
                <div class="focus-trap">
                  <button class="focus-element">First focusable</button>
                  <button class="focus-element">Second focusable</button>
                  <button class="focus-element">Last focusable</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Automatically manages keyboard focus for complex interactions</p>
          </div>

          <div class="a11y-pattern">
            <h4>Progressive Enhancement Interactions</h4>
            <div class="pattern-demo enhancement-demo">
              <div class="enhancement-layer">
                <button class="base-button">Basic Button</button>
                <button class="enhanced-button">Enhanced with Gestures</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Interactions that work without JavaScript but are enhanced with it</p>
          </div>

          <div class="a11y-pattern">
            <h4>Multi-Modal Input</h4>
            <div class="pattern-demo multimodal-demo">
              <div class="input-methods">
                <span class="input-icon">‚å®Ô∏è</span>
                <span class="input-icon">üëÜ</span>
                <span class="input-icon">üéôÔ∏è</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Same action achievable through multiple interaction methods</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="research-findings">
        <h2>Key Research Findings</h2>
        <div class="findings-grid">
          <div class="finding-item">
            <div class="finding-number">01</div>
            <div class="finding-content">
              <h4>Context Drives Pattern Success</h4>
              <p>The same interaction pattern can have vastly different effectiveness depending on user context, device, and task urgency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="finding-item">
            <div class="finding-number">02</div>
            <div class="finding-content">
              <h4>Accessibility Benefits Everyone</h4>
              <p>Patterns designed with accessibility in mind consistently performed better for all users, not just those with disabilities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="finding-item">
            <div class="finding-number">03</div>
            <div class="finding-content">
              <h4>Progressive Disclosure Wins</h4>
              <p>Interfaces that reveal complexity gradually had higher task completion rates and user satisfaction scores.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="finding-item">
            <div class="finding-number">04</div>
            <div class="finding-content">
              <h4>Micro-Interactions Create Connection</h4>
              <p>Well-crafted micro-interactions significantly improved emotional connection and perceived product quality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="future-implications">
        <h2>Implications for Design</h2>
        <div class="implications-content">
          <p>This research suggests a future where interaction patterns are more adaptive, inclusive, and contextually aware. Designers should focus on creating flexible systems rather than rigid interfaces.</p>
          
          <div class="recommendation-cards">
            <div class="recommendation">
              <h4>Design for Multiple Modalities</h4>
              <p>Every interaction should be achievable through multiple input methods</p>
            </div>
            <div class="recommendation">
              <h4>Embrace Progressive Enhancement</h4>
              <p>Start with accessible basics, then layer on enhanced experiences</p>
            </div>
            <div class="recommendation">
              <h4>Context-Aware Interfaces</h4>
              <p>Interfaces should adapt to user context, device capabilities, and environmental factors</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="concept-footer">
        <div class="concept-tags">
          <span class="tag">UX Research</span>
          <span class="tag">Interaction Design</span>
          <span class="tag">Accessibility</span>
          <span class="tag">Design Patterns</span>
          <span class="tag">User Testing</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="concept-nav">
          <a href="/blog/design-tokens" class="nav-link">Next ‚Üí</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  
  <BottomDrawer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .concept-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: white;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .concept-header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
  }

  .concept-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .back-link {
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: black;
  }

  .concept-details {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

